OL,3,CWidow of Hairy Biker looks ahead to
OL,4,C'Dave Day'
OL,6,FLiliana Orzahas was married to Dave
OL,7,FMyers for more than a decade.
OL,9,FThe widow of star Dave Myers hopes a
OL,10,Fday dedicated to the late TV chef will
OL,11,Fkeep his "energy" alive, as 10,000
OL,12,Fbikers prepare to descend on his
OL,13,Fhometown.
OL,15,FLiliana Orzahas helped organise ''
OL,16,Fwhich will be held in , Cumbria, on
OL,17,FSaturday, 8 June, to celebrate his
OL,18,Flife.
