OL,3,CWidow of Hairy Biker looks ahead to
OL,4,C'Dave Day'
OL,6,FMyers, who was part of the motorcycle-
OL,7,Friding cooking duo with co-presenter
OL,8,FSi King, , after he was diagnosed with
OL,9,Fcancer two years ago.
OL,11,FLiliana - who married Dave in 2011 -
OL,12,Fsays the idea to plan a day to
OL,13,Fremember her much loved husband came
OL,14,Fshortly after he passed.
OL,16,F"There was this comment on socials
OL,17,Fthat I picked up on," she said. "This
OL,18,Fperson was saying 'Brave Dave. Dave
OL,19,Fshould be synonymous to joy, zest for
OL,20,Flife'
