OL,3,CWidow of Hairy Biker looks ahead to
OL,4,C'Dave Day'
OL,6,F"So when we're having a good day, we
OL,7,Fshould say, 'I'm having a Dave day'."
OL,9,FShe told ITV's Lorraine: "Everybody
OL,10,Fwho loses somebody in their lives
OL,11,Fmisses them, but there's a different
OL,12,Flayer to it because if I turn on the
OL,13,FTV, he might be on.
OL,15,F"Cookbooks in the house everywhere,
OL,16,Fall of them stained with food."
OL,18,FShe added: "His energy is everywhere.
OL,19,FIt just transpires and rolls on into
OL,20,Fthis beautiful thing that's happening
OL,21,Fat the weekend."
