OL,3,CWidow of Hairy Biker looks ahead to
OL,4,C'Dave Day'
OL,6,F'Dave Day' will bring bikers together
OL,7,Ffrom across the country, and friends
OL,8,Fand fans of Dave in a heartfelt
OL,9,Ftribute.
OL,11,FThe ride is expected to be led by
OL,12,Ffellow Hairy Biker and friend Si King,
OL,13,Fwho will set off from from London to
OL,14,FBarrow-In-Furness, Cumbria.
OL,16,FOrganisers are predicting up to 10,000
OL,17,Fmotorcyclists will take part - with
OL,18,Fmany starting off in the capital and
OL,19,Fothers joining the convoy along the
OL,20,Froute.
