OL,3,CWidow of Hairy Biker looks ahead to
OL,4,C'Dave Day'
OL,6,FSpeaking on Instagram, Si said: "I'm
OL,7,Freally looking forward to seeing
OL,8,Feverybody on Saturday for the Dave Day
OL,9,FRide Out.
OL,11,F"I think we are going to have a great
OL,12,Fday and thank you all very much for
OL,13,Fall of the support.
OL,15,F"Be safe and be courteous to one
OL,16,Fanother and we'll have a smashing day."
OL,18,FWhen bikers arrive in Barrow, the town
OL,19,Fwill be an explosion of culture with
OL,20,Fevents, bands, plays, food stalls, and
OL,21,Fa concert taking place all day.
