OL,6,FThe event is raising money for the
OL,7,FInstitute for Cancer Research and
OL,8,FChildline.
OL,10,FWhat is the route for Dave Day?
OL,12,FOrganisers say timings are an estimate
OL,13,Fand may be subject to change due to
OL,14,Ftraffic and other factors:
OL,16,FAre there any road closures?
OL,18,FWestmorland and Furness Council says
OL,19,Froad closures will be in place around
OL,20,Fthe town hall - where large crowds
OL,21,Fwill gather in the afternoon.
