OL,4,C'Dave Day'
OL,6,FThe following road closures will be in
OL,7,Fplace from 3pm until 11pm on Saturday
OL,8,Fto support the event:
OL,10,FD-Day events will be taking place in
OL,11,Fthe morning to mark the 80th
OL,12,Fanniversary, and the staging will then
OL,13,Fbe used for Dave Day activities from
OL,14,F4pm onwards.
OL,16,FBarrow-in-Furness will be decorated in
OL,17,Fbunting specially Dave Day, with large
OL,18,Fcrowds expected to line the streets to
OL,19,Fsupport the biker procession.
