OL,3,CWidow of Hairy Biker looks ahead to
OL,4,C'Dave Day'
OL,6,FReflecting on the day, Liliana added:
OL,7,F"He's always been a very active
OL,8,Fperson. He's always been a very
OL,9,Fpositive person, and that carries on.
OL,11,F"I want to keep that growing. I want
OL,12,Fthe momentum to work still. Because
OL,13,Fthis is what he would have wanted."
